{"tid":2353281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】第四幢大廈遭「無辜強檢」　張竹君再道歉　區議員：一早講咗又唔理","createTime":"2021-01-04T15:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T15:14:56.000Z","uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea342f0276125f7464c3410703a103aa1bde4de","tid":2353281,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-第四幢大廈遭-無辜強檢-張竹君再道歉-區議員-一早講咗又唔理\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%A2%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E9%81%AD-%E7%84%A1%E8%BE%9C%E5%BC%B7%E6%AA%A2-%E5%BC%B5%E7%AB%B9%E5%90%9B%E5%86%8D%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A9%E8%AC%9B%E5%92%97%E5%8F%88%E5%94%94%E7%90%86&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=10ec8d4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%A2%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E9%81%AD-%E7%84%A1%E8%BE%9C%E5%BC%B7%E6%AA%A2-%E5%BC%B5%E7%AB%B9%E5%90%9B%E5%86%8D%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A9%E8%AC%9B%E5%92%97%E5%8F%88%E5%94%94%E7%90%86&h=8cd34a80\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-第四幢大廈遭-無辜強檢-張竹君再道歉-區議員-一早講咗又唔理</a><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kt-29_Mf8z8_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkt-29_Mf8z8_1200x0.png&h=2a3584ca&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n再有大廈「無辜被強檢」，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今日（4 日）在記者會上表示，誤將觀塘華峰園個案計算進葵涌華豐園，令葵涌華豐園被發強制檢測令。張竹君為事件致歉，但表示葵涌華豐園的強制檢測令已到最後一天，因此不會撤銷檢測令，但不會對該大廈執法。葵涌區議員張鈞翹批評，自己早於強制檢測令發出前，已向衞生防護中心查詢，「講咗畀你都唔理，咁即係當耳邊風啦？」觀塘區議員蘇冠聰則直斥「冇可能擺咁大烏龍」，「會唔會有其他地方都係咁？」<br />\n<br />\n葵涌華豐園早前被指在 14 日內，有兩個單位出現無關連確診個案，分別為編號 7635 及 7938 的年老夫婦及編號 8633 女子，因此在上周六被發出強制檢測令，要求居民於今日（4 日）或之前完成強制檢測。不過，張竹君今日表示，誤將觀塘「華峰園」個案計入葵涌「華豐園」，令葵涌華豐園被發強制檢測令。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君澄清，兩棟大廈各自只有一個單位受影響，不符合檢測準則，又為搞亂兩座大廈致歉。不過，她表示，由於葵涌華豐園的強制檢測令今日到期，故不會撤銷該大廈的強制檢測令，但往後不會就強制檢測對該大廈有任何執法。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>區議員：發強檢令前已向中心查詢</strong><br />\n<br />\n葵涌區議員張鈞翹向《立場》表示，其實早於上周四（12 月 29 日），他已引述葵涌華豐園管理處，指未見有人被接走，編號 7635 個案的活動範圍亦主要在觀塘區，因此向中心查詢，惟中心當時沒有回應，翌日更發出強制檢測令，直至今日才確認兩個個案不屬葵涌華豐園。他批評中心的溝通混亂，「問你又十問九唔應，講咗畀你都唔理，照出強制檢測，咁即係當耳邊風啦？」<br />\n<br />\n他又質疑，自己今日再致電了解後，對方在 5 分鐘後已確認事件，「咁你即係一早知啦？但又主動唔講」。<br />\n<br />\n至於該兩個個案所在的觀塘華峰園，該區區議員蘇冠聰直斥衞生防護中心「好錯，冇可能擺咁大烏龍」，「入醫院都要寫 full address 啦，無可能搞錯，仲要連續搞錯兩個？」、「好多嘢都係睇確診地址去做&hellip;&hellip;會唔會有其他地方搞錯但唔知？」<br />\n<br />\n日前張竹君已曾公布，觀塘曉麗苑曉星閣、將軍澳翠林邨安林樓及青衣青華苑華欣閣，經調查後發現不符合強檢準則，因此會剔出名單，並就安排混亂致歉。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n道歉有撚用? Damage is done. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衞生署一錯再錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強制檢測係人禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日監察衞生署有冇老屈大廈做強制檢測</span></strong></p><br />\n[求推] 衞生署 強制檢測名單 又双叒叕有錯？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">　強制檢測係人禍<br />\n　大廈名單成日錯</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278472d672b36ce7f03d0c6fb79c11096a441f85","tid":2353281,"uid":51754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日監察衞生署有冇老屈大廈做強制檢測</span></strong></p><br />\n[求推] 衞生署 強制檢測名單 又双叒叕有錯？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"> 強制檢測係人禍<br />\n 大廈名單成日錯</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"278472d672b36ce7f03d0c6fb79c11096a441f85","tid":2353281,"uid":51754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日監察衞生署有冇老屈大廈做強制檢測</span></strong></p><br />\n[求推] 衞生署 強制檢測名單 又双叒叕有錯？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a><br />\n<br />\